{"_path":"/resident/r034","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"樂善國小生活圈 社區營造規劃 - 公園篇","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r034-02.png","sequence":34,"category":"社區營造","place":"樂善國小生活圈","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-06-06T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"樂善國小生活圈-社區營造規劃-公園篇"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小生活圈 社區營造規劃 - 公園篇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"主旨"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主旨"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美化活用畸零地, 縫補並串接現有公園打造完整的樂善國小生活圈綠色廊帶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小生活圈現有 文德, 公 20, 長樂(公 19) 及樂善四個公園。 其中文德公園及公 20 公園都屬於廊帶型公園。 沿樂學路貫穿樂善國小生活圈, 是宜居環境的主要憑藉。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可惜目前區域內有許多私有畸零地, 成了雜草區或環境保護區上游的種菜區。 這些私有地往往被拋擲垃圾成為生活圈內的"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"環境毒瘤"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 是蚊蠅, 蛇鼠藏身之地。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝龜山區公所, 陳雅倫議員 及 李宗豪議員 都已注意到此問題分別展開改善行動。 本文是希望匯總所有規劃案, 並收集居民, 社區管委會 及 里長 持續提供的規劃意見, 期望共同推動整合型社區營造計畫。 讓樂善國小生活圈成為 A7 重劃區的公園綠地建設標竿。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-02.png","src":"/images/resident/r034-02.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"規劃匯總"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"規劃匯總"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"衛星公園的串接措施"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 樂捷段 147 地號"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提案者: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1GJzRbmWwx/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫議員"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n方案:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將樂捷段 147 號地, 設置為公 20 公園的附屬停車場及兒童遊戲區。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將樂學路的路邊停車遷移至上述公園附屬停車場。 讓樂學路能增加車道, 使得區域主要路線樂學路交通能夠順暢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在樂善段 176 號地附近, 除了李宗豪議員的規劃, 雅倫注意到私有畸零地的垃圾對附近樂善國小及文德幼兒園的隱患！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫將要求市府用都市發展基金取得附近私有畸零地, 整理此區域為遊戲場及公園。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-11b.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r034-11b.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂捷段 147 號地"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-11c.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r034-11c.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善段 176 號地"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. 樂善段 176 地號"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提案者: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/177MD3XvBD/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪議員"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n方案:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善段 176 地號為公有土地, 宗豪邀集警察局、都發局、交通局、區公所、當地里長等多個單位現勘，爭取將這塊地重新活化利用，目前已經提報中央爭取到經費補助，準備啟動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"初步規劃，將會整合周邊綠地，規劃兒童遊具、行人步道、斜坡道等無障礙設施，透過公共空間的重整，縫補城市節點，讓新舊城區的生活空間重新串連起來，打造真正走得進、用得到的社區綠廊。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-12.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r034-12.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. 保護區上游"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提案者：龜山區公所, 請參考\n依據: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://web.pcc.gov.tw/tps/atm/AtmAwardWithoutSso/QueryAtmAwardDetail?pkAtmMain=NzA4Mzg1MDU%3D&fbclid=IwY2xjawKdH5BleHRuA2FlbQIxMABicmlkETF1VE1OV2JpSHlBcGtnc0FvAR4Iypwnv0xWgXCI7APxDv0iKI9FmOD5wSu57Qb95HdUuNNILkz7j7TZfCDqkQ_aem_ejqswEBZsjcZKq45ZYziQQ"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"政府電子採購網 公開標案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n資料:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 282 萬"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"施工日期 2025/03/25 - 2026/02/27 (預估)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 龜山區樂善里綠廊串聯改善工程"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"詳細改善內容待釐清！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r034-13.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r034-13.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"居民建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"